        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28273164/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28273164/" class="">第254页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/taxiliya/" class=" " title="风起湘江">风起湘江</a>
                (你瞅啥？)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="28273164">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">「殷仲文天才宏贍」條[校箋]②：博亮，疑作「傅亮」。宋書、南史本傳均無此語。孝標失考，但有「亮別見」語。

您老下结论可真痛快啊。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-08-25 21:56</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                「殷仲文天才宏贍」條[校箋]②：<blockquote><q>博亮，疑作「傅亮」。宋書、南史本傳均無此語。孝標失考，但有「亮別見」語。</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>您老下结论可真痛快啊。
